**Summary:** This documentation explains three methods for creating cohorts in Amplitude: using Microscope to create static or behavioral cohorts from data points, importing static cohorts from CSV files containing user IDs or Amplitude IDs, and creating inline behavioral cohorts with interval filtering directly within the Segmentation module of chart types.

